<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 08 at 4:29AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Southwest Montana Snow Showers Reducing Visibility...
Bands of snow showers are moving across Southwest Montana this
morning. These bands will be capable of briefly reducing
visibility to a half-mile or less. Snow accumulation associated
with these bands should be less than a half an inch. Be vigilant
for quickly changing conditions if traveling this morning.</description>
